Class GCMConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.speedtools.services.push.implementation.gcm.GCMConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PushNotificationProvider

    public class GCMConnector
extends Object
implements PushNotificationProvider
    Connector that is able to push messages for Google Cloud Messaging. This should be a singleton in the context of a single thread because it maintains state.

        @Nonnull
public Set<PushToken> getObsoletePushTokens()
        Description copied from interface: PushNotificationProvider
        This method returns push channel IDs that have been used earlier, but which are considered to be no longer valid, according to the push notification provider. This will happen when a customer removes an application from its device for instance. References can safely be removed.
